{"tid":1199411,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日unfriend咗唔少IG","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:08:21.000Z","uid":236148,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bb08fe5f411e12adab80fa817775ecea4b5041a6","tid":1199411,"uid":236148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:07:33.000Z","msg":"有啲係唔熟嘅朋友 有啲係大同中同小同<br />\n<br />\n其中一個 唔熟嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今次送中條例係好貼身嘅事 無藉口可以唔關心不聞不問 係WhatsApp group講下件事 都可以無咩人一齊討論<br />\n<br />\n琴晚都有留守到3點 但我真係有包袱 走咗先<br />\n今朝睇到個358位義士 幾百個後生仔 有巴打上嚟講佢好驚 我真係喊咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解可以有人咁是非不分 不問不聞 置身事外？<br />\n<br />\n仲有機會 唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a67152d3a70eb00e7677167b579a047ac2fe7f","tid":1199411,"uid":36702,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"只睇cctvb嘅弱智咪會唔識分析 <br />\n<br />\nsend下其他文同相比佢睇下"},{"pid":"5de3290d301fe4968cb8c98c1be673a910f2430e","tid":1199411,"uid":236148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"40a67152d3a70eb00e7677167b579a047ac2fe7f","tid":1199411,"uid":36702,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:08:59.000Z","msg":"只睇cctvb嘅弱智咪會唔識分析 <br />\n<br />\nsend下其他文同相比佢睇下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"你嚟啦 佢IG public 嘅<br />\n已經唔想同佢講嘢了"},{"pid":"7a637cfb67cce8428a4c18aeba8cf0fa2a5136fe","tid":1199411,"uid":236148,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有一個"},{"pid":"50a93035f6be65cc575afabf60f4043884b3039c","tid":1199411,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26e54db3271486c2